                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "While most other parkour mods are mutually exclusive (i.e., Mobilize and Lightning Dash cannot be equipped at the same time), Anguish mods are compatible with other parkour mods."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Nira's Anguish",
                  "pageId": 1555300,
                  "revisionId": 2787967,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "When Nira's Anguish and another parkour mod are equipped, the effects of both mods are combined."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Nira's Anguish",
                  "pageId": 1555300,
                  "revisionId": 2787967,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, equipping Nira's Anguish and Mobilize at max rank would result in a total of +35% Parkour Velocity."
                }
              },
